Enum AnchorText

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<AnchorText>
org.apache.juneau.html.AnchorText
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<AnchorText>, java.lang.constant.Constable
public enum AnchorText
extends java.lang.Enum<AnchorText>
Identifies possible values for the HtmlSerializer.Builder.uriAnchorText(AnchorText) setting.
